defaults
default in economic performance between cities, how much of that is explained by differences in connectivity, based on real world examples out there today, and we have asked what difference HS2 will make to that, and, therefore, what difference HS2 can make to the productivity of the UK economy. It is very considered, based on the best available evidence today.
