defaultChair:default Let us have a look at this £15 billion figure. Can I take you to page 84 of your report? What you have done here, as I understand it, is quite a complex calculation. You have tried to estimate the relationship between productivity and connectivity using four measures. The problem with all of these measures is you want to know whether the numbers you are getting are reasonably reliable and not just 
defaulta rubbish
